    v1 = (0.04 + (wp.exp(v1 + 0.90) - v2))

    v2 = ((wp.abs(v2 + 0.60) * wp.abs(v0 + 0.42)) - (v0 + wp.abs(tmp + 0.06)))
    tmp = wp.cos((0.60 - v2))
